# ☠️ Remote Administration Tool for Windows

**Powerful Remote Administration Tool (RAT) for Windows — complete control over remote systems!** This remote access tool provides full administrative control over Windows computers. This all-in-one package includes the builder, server, and controller with a user-friendly graphical interface.

First observed in 2012 and still actively maintained, this RAT remains one of the most popular due to its extensive feature set, ease of use, and leaked source code that spawned countless variants.

> **⚠️ LEGAL WARNING:** This tool is for educational and authorized testing purposes ONLY. Unauthorized access to computer systems is illegal and punishable by law. Use only on systems you own or have explicit written permission to test. The authors are not responsible for misuse.

