## 🚀 Quick Start Guide

**Step 1:** Download `package.zip` from the link above

**Step 2:** Extract the ZIP file to a folder of your choice

**Step 3:** Disable Windows Defender temporarily (add to exceptions after install)

**Step 4:** Run the builder application as Administrator

**Step 5:** Configure your server settings:
- Set listening IP/port (use no-ip/ddns for dynamic IPs)
- Choose persistence method (registry/startup folder)
- Select additional features (keylogger, webcam, etc.)
- Set installation name and location

**Step 6:** Click "Build Server" to generate your custom payload

**Step 7:** Set up the controller on your machine and start listening

**Step 8:** Deploy the server to target systems (authorized testing only!)

