| **Notification Functions** | Message boxes, speech synthesis, beeps |
| **Plugin System** | Load plugins for extended functionality |

---

## 📊 Technical Details

**Architecture:**
- Written in .NET framework
- Reverse backdoor connection model
- C2 communication over configurable ports
- Encoded traffic to evade detection

**Persistence Methods:**
- Registry Run keys
- Startup folder shortcuts
- Scheduled tasks

**Defense Evasion:**
- Can disable Windows Firewall
- Can disable System Restore
- Can disable Task Manager
- Can disable Registry Editor
- Can be obfuscated using third-party tools

