## 🔧 Builder Configuration Options

| Setting | Options | Description |
|---------|---------|-------------|
| **Connection Type** | TCP / UDP | Protocol for communication |
| **Host** | IP or DDNS | Server address (use DDNS for dynamic IPs) |
| **Port** | 1-65535 | Listening port |
| **Install Name** | Custom | Filename for installed server |
| **Install Path** | %AppData%, %Temp%, System32 | Installation location |
| **Persistence** | Registry / Startup / Both | How to survive reboots |
| **Mutex** | Custom | Prevent multiple instances |
| **Icon** | Custom .ico | Change executable appearance |
| **File Binder** | Optional | Bind with legitimate files |
| **USB Spread** | On/Off | Auto-copy to removable drives |

